com.bbn.openmap.graphicLoader.netmap
Interface NetMapConstants

All Known Implementing Classes:
NetMapConnector, NetMapGraphicLoader, NetMapReader
public interface NetMapConstants

This interface describes the different constant settings used for the NetMapEvent properties. If you implement this class, you have direct access to the constants.
